data.enText: the same; in a similar way

data.chText: 他投票赞成变革并期望他的同事投同样的票。
data.enText: He voted for the change and he expected his colleagues to do likewise .

data.chText: 她的第二次婚姻也不幸福。
data.enText: Her second marriage was likewise unhappy.

data.chText: （表示感觉相同）我也是，我有同感
data.enText: used to show that you feel the same towards sb or about sth

data.chText: “你要是需要帮助就告诉我。”“你也一样。”
data.enText: ‘Let me know if you ever need any help.’ ‘Likewise.’

means: (表示感觉相同)我也是，我有同感

example: parents and teachers alike demanded reforms
some people have little power to do good, and have likewise little strength to resist evil"- Samuel Johnso

value.def: You use likewise when you are comparing two methods, states, or situations and saying that they are similar.

example.ex: These requests are ignored. His requests for rent are likewise sometimes ignored...
example.tran: 这些要求被置之不理。他关于支付租金的要求有时也同样未被理睬。

example.ex: The V2 was not an ordinary weapon: it could only be used against cities. Likewise the atom bomb.
example.tran: V2火箭并非普通武器：它只能用于对付城市。原子弹也是这样。

gramarinfo.label: ADV with v, ADV with cl/group

value.def: If you do something and someone else does likewise, they do the same or a similar thing.

example.ex: He lent money, made donations and encouraged others to do likewise.
example.tran: 他又借钱又捐款捐物，并且鼓励别人也这样做。
